## .dockerignore - keep the build context lean
## Build context is the solution root (templates/Aspire/MinimalApi/)

# Build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Test artifacts
**/TestResults/
**/*.trx
**/coverage/

# IDE and tooling
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.userprefs
**/*.DotSettings.user

# Git
.git/
.gitattributes
.gitignore
.buildkit-cache/

# Docs and CI (not needed in the image)
.github/
Infra/
**/*.md
!MinimalApi/appsettings*.json

# Secrets and local config (NEVER bake into image)
**/secrets.json
**/*.pfx
**/*.pem
**/*.key

# Docker itself
**/Dockerfile*
**/.dockerignore

# Test projects (not deployed)
MinimalApi.Core.Tests/

